.TH DDTP-TRANSLATE 1 "2026-02-15" "Daniel Nylander" "DDTP Translate Manual"
.SH NAME
ddtp-translate - Translate Debian package descriptions via DDTP
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B ddtp-translate
.SH DESCRIPTION
\fBddtp-translate\fR is a GTK4/Adwaita application for translating Debian package descriptions via DDTP. It provides a side-by-side editor with original English descriptions and translation area, direct DDTP submission via email, configurable SMTP settings, local caching, search and filter, and statistics per language.
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
.B \-\-help
Show help message and exit.
.SH FILES
.TP
.I ~/.config/ddtp-translate/
Configuration files.
.TP
.I ~/.cache/ddtp-translate/
Cached data.
